text: @fedex Your Hollywood location is an actual joke.  Printers always offline. Card readers don’t work. Never enough staff, not to mention they all seem miserable. Shouldn’t this be a flagship location. Need some serious attention - been this bad for months
@notsofastfood Hello Bob, my name is Mary. I apologize as this is not the experience we would like to provide. Please DM  the location address and I will look into to this for you.

@notsofastfood Hi, my name is Bobby. I am sorry to hear you are displeased with your FedEx experience. The FedEx Office team hours are Monday-Friday, 7:00 AM-8:00 PM CT, and Saturday, 7:00 AM-6:00 PM CT. The team will respond upon its return.

@notsofastfood Hi, this is Letricia.  I apologize for the inconvenience. At FedEx Office we strive to provide our customers with prompt, courteous, and professional service, and take it very serious when we fail to meet these standards. Your comments were forwarded to management for resolution.
@notsofastfood If you would like a follow up call regarding your concern, please reply to this message with your phone number.  Letricia
